Moving around with h = left, l = right, j = down, k = up. 
Use 'i' to insert text.
Use 'a' to append text.
0 (zero) to go at the begining of the line
d to delete: w a word e to the end of the current word
d$ to delete to the end of the line from current cursor position.
d2w will delete two words
dd will dele curent line
2dd delete two lines
u to undo once and U to undo the whole line also C-r (Ctrl+r) to redo

